{
  "stem": "20083.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only have this information from the International Tracing Service in Arolsen in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got it in writing exactly when they were deported, with which--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they-- Gestapo, they call it Geheime Staatspolizei transport, or Judentransport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The date was actually listed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in my father's case, I think even-- in my grandmother's too, in Hamburg-- my mother's mother, Marie Fraenkel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The date, actually-- the date of death when they were either killed or when they died in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm still in England.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister knew-- no, actually, it wasn't my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My cousin, who still lives in Hamburg, knew a German actress in this country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her name's Uta Hagen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she's quite a well-known stage actress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's played in very few movies, but mostly stage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she's also a teacher at the Bergdorf-Hagen School of Acting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Ilse Fraenkel, in Hamburg, introduced-- sent a letter of introduction to Uta Hagen and said, please see Anne Marie Kuttner in New York at this and this address.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And maybe she can help you find a sponsor who will help me get from England to the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my sister saw her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They became friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Uta Hagen helped me with the affidavit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I arrived about a year later, already, from England.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the date of my arrival in the States was December the 8th, 1947.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at first, the first week or two, I think until Christmas or so, I stayed with my sister.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, because I knew somebody in England by the name of Lyersh Biero-- he was well-known scriptwriter for Sir Alexander Korda.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was also a friend of Leslie Howard's, who-- with whom I became friendly.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
